<dl id="n12044j"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12044j">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12044j"> 44(j)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> preached 3 days long</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">&hellip; on one occasion &hellip; the Saint interpreted the four Evangelists, for three days and nights; the people were so entranced and spellbound by his inspired eloquence, that the time seemed to them but as the space of one day&ldquo;. <small> Very Rev. Dean Kinane, <a name="TKSP" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#TKSP"><cite title="source">St. Patrick: his life, his heroic virtues, his labours, and the fruits of his labours</cite></a>, (ed. unknown) 209</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
